Class Enquiry

java.lang.Object
BTOManagementSystem.Model.Enquiry
public class Enquiry extends Object
Represents an enquiry submitted by an applicant for a BTO project.

An enquiry includes the project it refers to, the applicant's NRIC, the question content, the officer and manager handling it, and the reply if available.

      public Enquiry(String enquiryID, String projectName, String applicantNRIC, String question, String officerIC, String managerIC)
      Constructs an enquiry without an answer (used when creating a new enquiry).
      Parameters:
      enquiryID - the unique ID of the enquiry
      projectName - the name of the project related to the enquiry
      applicantNRIC - the NRIC of the applicant
      question - the question content
      officerIC - the NRIC of the officer assigned to respond
      managerIC - the NRIC of the manager overseeing the project
